description._content: Description: Three Present-Day Stud Sires, "Springfield" Flock. Sir William. Location: New South Wales, Sydney, Australia Date: 1877 ------------------------------------------------------ Description: Three Present-Day Stud Sires, "Springfield" Flock. Centennial., by Sir William. Bred by A. Lucian Faithfull, Sprindfield. Weight of Fleece, 22lbs., 365 days' growth. Grass fed and unhoused, 1922. Aged 5 years. Location: New South Wales, Sydney, Australia Date: 1877 ------------------------------------------------------ Description: Three Present-Day Stud Sires, "Springfield" Flock. Commercial Junior. Bred by A. Lucain Faithfull. Weight of Fleece, 20lbs, 365 days' growth. Aged 3 years. Grass fed: unboused; 1922. Location: New South Wales, Sydney, Australia Date: 1877 ------------------------------------------------------ Our Catalogue Reference: Part of CO 1069/611.
